flowchart TB
  %% ===== OFFLINE =====
  subgraph OFF[Offline: Data and Training Pipeline]
    direction LR
    D[(Source Dataset)] --> SPLIT[Split: Train / Validate / Test]

    SPLIT --> PRE_TR[Preprocessing Train\n- Handle missing values\n- Convert target to numeric]
    SPLIT --> PRE_VA[Preprocessing Validate\n- Handle missing values\n- Convert target to numeric]
    SPLIT --> PRE_TE[Preprocessing Test\n- Handle missing values\n- Convert target to numeric]

    PRE_TR --> TG[TimeGAN\nSynthetic augmentation]
    TG --> HM_TRAIN[Train Hybrid\nFuzzy -> Transformer -> Bi-LSTM]

    PRE_TR --> BM_TRAIN[Train Baselines\nLSTM / TCN / PatchTST]
    PRE_VA --> HM_TRAIN
    PRE_VA --> BM_TRAIN

    HM_TRAIN --> SEL[Model selection and calibration]
    BM_TRAIN --> SEL
    SEL --> ART[(Model artifacts and metadata)]
  end

  %% ===== ONLINE =====
  subgraph ON[Online: Serving and Inference]
    direction LR
    ART --> API[FastAPI Backend\nMODEL_STATE and shared services]

    U[User] --> FE[Frontend Next.js\nRatingForm / Reports / Methodology]
    FE --> PRED[POST /api/predict\nfeatures]
    PRED --> TLSTM[TLSTMFuzzy Predictor]
    TLSTM --> API

    FE --> HIST[POST /api/history]
    HIST --> PH[(prediction_history.csv)]

    FE --> EXPL[POST /api/explain]
    EXPL --> GX[Gemini Explainer]
    GX --> GA[Gemini API]

    API --> RESP[PredictResult\n- rating\n- probabilities\n- confidence\n- risk_score]
    GA --> RESP
    RESP --> FE
    FE --> UO[Display output\nIG / HY / Distressed + risk interpretation]
    UO --> U
  end

  PRE_TE --> EVAL[Final test evaluation\nIG / HY / Distressed]
  EVAL --> ART

  classDef data fill:#e8f5ff,stroke:#2b6cb0,stroke-width:1px
  classDef train fill:#fff3d6,stroke:#b7791f,stroke-width:1px
  classDef serve fill:#eafbea,stroke:#2f855a,stroke-width:1px
  classDef ext fill:#f4ecff,stroke:#6b46c1,stroke-width:1px

  class D,PH,ART data
  class PRE_TR,PRE_VA,PRE_TE,TG,HM_TRAIN,BM_TRAIN,SEL,EVAL train
  class FE,API,PRED,HIST,EXPL,TLSTM,RESP,U,UO serve
  class GX,GA ext
